12. Grievance Redressal Mission

Target stakeholders: EPFO staff, members, helpdesk teams
Game format: Service delivery simulation

The player manages a grievance desk. Citizens raise issues such as claim rejection, passbook mismatch, transfer delay, KYC pending, pension problem, or employer not depositing contribution.

The player must ask the right questions, identify correct category, check records, escalate if needed, and close the grievance with a proper response.

Learning outcomes:

Improves quality of grievance replies and member communication.

Gamification:

Citizen satisfaction score, resolution time score, empathy score, reopening penalty.
